      <description>&lt;p&gt;Season 2 of a project, which was (and is) inspired by &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/una/personal-goals&#34;&gt;Una Kravets&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The goal is to share my personal learning efforts, making them explicit &amp;amp; open.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In high school I had the epiphany that it is better to follow good teachers then good topics. Throughout my studies I tried to follow that maxim as good as possible, but forgot about it recently. This year I want to re-establish my principle once more.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;With that in mind I ordered the learning stuff into 3 categories.&lt;/p&gt;

